text: The Waikerie Football Club is an Australian rules football club which compete in the Riverland Football League. The club was formed in 1908 and was a foundation member of the Mid Murray FL in 1910. It split into two teams in 1927 only to reform in 1929 and entered the Upper Murray "A" grade competition.The encyclopedia of South Australian Country Football Clubs. ==Premierships== *1911, 1912, 1913, 1926, 1934, 1936, 1974, 1991, 1993, 1994, 2001, 2003, 2005, 2007, 2014, 2016, 2017, 2018 ==Notable players== * Mark Ricciuto * Brad Helbig * Luke Jericho ==Books== * The encyclopedia of South Australian Country Football Clubs.
